### Crear tercero — persona natural
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/thirds HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "thirdPartyTypeId": 17,
    "documentTypeId": 21,
    "documentNumber": "1234567890",
    "firstName": "Juan",
    "secondName": "Pablo",
    "firstLastName": "García",
    "secondLastName": "López",
    "birthDate": "1990-05-15",
    "sexId": 7,
    "genderId": 11,
    "maritalStatusId": 15,
    "educationLevelId": 21,
    "birthCountryId": 19,
    "birthMunicipalityId": 139,
    "observations": "Paciente referido"
}

###

### Crear tercero — persona jurídica (pagador/EPS)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/thirds HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "thirdPartyTypeId": 19,
    "documentTypeId": 28,
    "documentNumber": "900123456",
    "verificationDigit": "7",
    "companyName": "EPS Salud Total S.A.",
    "observations": "EPS principal"
}

###

### Crear tercero — profesional de salud
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/thirds HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "thirdPartyTypeId": 18,
    "documentTypeId": 21,
    "documentNumber": "9876543210",
    "firstName": "María",
    "firstLastName": "Rodríguez",
    "secondLastName": "Pérez",
    "birthDate": "1985-03-20",
    "sexId": 8,
    "genderId": 11,
    "birthCountryId": 19,
    "birthMunicipalityId": 139
}

###

### Obtener tercero por ID
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/thirds/8 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Buscar tercero por tipo y número de documento (exacto)
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/thirds/by-document?documentTypeId=1&documentNumber=1234567890 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar terceros (sin búsqueda)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/thirds/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "",
    "order_by": "t.nombre_completo",
    "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Listar terceros — búsqueda por nombre (ignora tildes y mayúsculas)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/thirds/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "garcia",
    "order_by": "t.nombre_completo",
    "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Listar terceros — búsqueda por número de documento
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/thirds/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "1234567890",
    "order_by": "t.nombre_completo",
    "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Activar / Inactivar tercero (toggle)
PATCH http://localhost:{{port}}/api/thirds/1/toggle-active HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
